Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！依文
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依文…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.53,0:00:13.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡呢  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.28,0:00:17.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Malleus Aquilonis{\r}\N冰神戰鎚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.07,0:00:30.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:32.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.40,0:00:39.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由依文同學組織的地獄訓練終於告一段落
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.42,0:00:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.78,0:00:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就代表是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.05,0:00:46.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.01,0:00:49.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.23,0:00:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們涅吉魔社正在享受海邊的短暫休假
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:59.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉小弟是第一次來日本的海邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.10,0:01:02.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  人可真不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:05.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:08.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就像我們當初約定好的那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.48,0:01:10.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好玩個痛快哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩個盡興
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.89,0:01:14.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.79,0:01:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:17.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:17.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.20,0:01:19.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易來趟海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:21.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不游泳豈不是白來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.47,0:01:25.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來和我比比看誰先游到那邊的岩石吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.40,0:01:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.98,0:01:28.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要比
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.05,0:01:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的海灘熱鬧非凡  大家說是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.46,0:01:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…為什麼班長也在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:41.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡說起來可是涅吉魔社（暫定）的合宿活動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.37,0:01:43.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼連你們這些人也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.57,0:01:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果班長和裕奈  以及蒔繪她們也都跟來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.74,0:01:56.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寶貝們可真是活力無限啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.01,0:01:58.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  你們不能跟過來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.23,0:02:01.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道會遇到什麼危險的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.19,0:02:02.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可真是死腦筋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.46,0:02:04.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.94,0:02:07.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們不跟你們去那些危險的地方就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這倒是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.73,0:02:11.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.33,0:02:12.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼定下來喵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.20,0:02:12.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.08,0:02:15.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個暑假  我們大家一起去英國
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.16,0:02:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.22,0:02:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂！  別自作主張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.27,0:02:25.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此這般  最後還是決定了大家一起去英國
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.17,0:02:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為這樣騷動總算是平息了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.69,0:02:34.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長  小蒔等人  她們基本上都是知道涅吉弟弟的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.48,0:02:37.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才一起跟去威爾士的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:43.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們二位在去威爾士之前  最好也先考慮些深層接觸涅吉弟弟的方案比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.58,0:02:44.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.39,0:02:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥…深層接觸…？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們很走運地瞭解了\N關於涅吉弟弟的魔法和他的過去  這就是你們的優勢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.92,0:02:56.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光知道傻玩的話  搞不好會讓誰把涅吉弟弟給搶走哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.81,0:04:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話…話是這麼說…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.46,0:04:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  我們能學會魔法  並且站在能直接幫助涅吉老師的立場上這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:48.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實是純屬偶然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.94,0:04:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小蒔就很可愛  真是羡慕她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.99,0:04:56.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班長也是賽過模特般的好身材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.58,0:04:58.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且為人正直清廉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:01.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩個人要是動真格的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.20,0:05:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也許沒什麼勝算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和香你還好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.58,0:05:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我根本就是一副慘不忍睹的狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊  感覺未來好暗淡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:17.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老師身邊還有明日菜同學在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.16,0:05:19.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:22.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學她又是怎麼想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.56,0:05:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.49,0:05:29.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.63,0:05:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:34.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅…涅吉老師和明日菜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人獨處難不成是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地獄特訓之後的放鬆真是格外舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.77,0:05:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.91,0:05:46.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天非常感謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.26,0:05:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹…幹嘛啊  突然一本正經地…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.91,0:05:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要感謝也應該感謝大伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是班長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:58.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙知道你的目的之後  就非常關心這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前一陣子的那些情報也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.91,0:06:02.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:07.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然那兩個人之間的關係當中有一些特殊的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.00,0:06:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.74,0:06:15.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然那究竟算不算是戀愛類的感情這一點上還有商討餘地…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:19.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然聽不太明白  總之就是說他們兩個人在打情罵俏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.98,0:06:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  和香你…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.43,0:06:23.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那話不是我說的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.36,0:06:27.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受不了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.04,0:06:30.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我辛辛苦苦大老遠跑來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.00,0:06:35.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他卻和那傻呼呼的的女人卿卿我我纏纏綿綿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.60,0:06:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管什麼時候涅吉他都傻得要命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.49,0:06:41.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:44.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fortress Ra Tes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Release Lilios
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.76,0:06:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅～吉！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.82,0:06:55.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Anya Flame Buster Kick{\r}\N阿妮亞火焰超級踢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.18,0:07:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞搞搞啥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召來！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.71,0:07:10.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她一下子衝過來想做什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.51,0:07:11.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我們的敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.17,0:07:14.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…剛剛那招…莫非是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  表現不錯嘛  居然能避開剛剛那一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.21,0:07:20.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來魔法的修行你從來都沒有偷過懶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一點沒變啊  小不點外加傻呼呼的涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.41,0:07:26.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:28.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！阿妮亞難道就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.69,0:07:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼阿妮亞會來日本？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.05,0:07:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不應該在倫敦當占卜師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會來這裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.35,0:07:36.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這還用問嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.26,0:07:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是來帶你回…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.28,0:07:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的披風怎麼著火了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件好貴的說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.12,0:07:48.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.58,0:07:51.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燙燙燙燙燙  不好了  屁股著火了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救火救火  快來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.77,0:07:54.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.82,0:07:56.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿…阿妮亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.82,0:08:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是來做什麼的啊  阿妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是來帶你回去的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.47,0:08:09.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個閒不住的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢話少說  趕快跟我回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:15.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去？  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:16.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還問為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.91,0:08:20.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放了暑假你還是不回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.64,0:08:24.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才代替寂寞的涅佳涅姐姐來找你回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.73,0:08:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.67,0:08:26.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶我回去？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞好像是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.70,0:08:32.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  她是涅吉故鄉村落裡那個小大人的青梅竹馬…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了的話就趕快跟我回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:36.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.28,0:08:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我特意去了一趟麻帆良學園  結果你還不在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:45.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧我還特意去調查一番  跑來這個土氣的國家的土氣的海灘找你的說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:47.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快跟我走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.31,0:08:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.03,0:08:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  阿妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.50,0:08:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉他回英國之前還有事要辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:56.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且現在涅吉擔任顧問的部團正在這裡進行合宿活動
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:58.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能再稍微等一等？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.49,0:09:03.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個一來就跟人套近乎的女人  我記得是叫神樂坂明日菜的那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:06.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…照片上最常出現的…最需要留心的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.63,0:09:09.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一見面就被她看到失態的一面…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.50,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（阿妮亞的主觀視點）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:13.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這什麼身材啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.06,0:09:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說涅吉他就是因為這個才不願意回去的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.51,0:09:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說她是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:22.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人呢！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.82,0:09:24.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.26,0:09:26.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫阿妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.34,0:09:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家涅吉讓你多費心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.76,0:09:31.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不必客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.54,0:09:33.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面  阿妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:38.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說來  一見面就耍出那種魔法招數  還客氣個什麼勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.39,0:09:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是請放心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後涅吉就由我來照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.80,0:09:45.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  就這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.38,0:09:46.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.14,0:09:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.82,0:09:50.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞趕這麼久的路也累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.24,0:09:53.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少先吃個飯再走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:56.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺…刺身  還有天婦羅這裡都吃得到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刺身…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.53,0:10:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天婦羅…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.37,0:10:10.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老師的青梅竹馬？！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.90,0:10:11.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.42,0:10:16.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…好像單純只是來叫涅吉早點回老家的樣子…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.33,0:10:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同年齡的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:21.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來稍微年長一歲的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.31,0:10:22.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可愛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.91,0:10:23.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美女？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.40,0:10:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.56,0:10:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我也看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好豐盛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:40.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些全部吃掉都可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.02,0:10:43.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.41,0:10:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？  好全新的觸感
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都吃這些的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:50.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羡慕
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.91,0:10:52.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本美食最棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.32,0:10:54.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.38,0:10:57.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊…不是小孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.91,0:10:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,輪不到你來說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.45,0:11:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢…涅吉弟弟的青梅竹馬  當然是小孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:05.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.88,0:11:07.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下可算是沒白來一趟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  竟然會為刺身和天婦羅上鉤
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞真是貪吃鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火大
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:15.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.82,0:11:21.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不是因為你總是不回去  才害我特地跑來這個土裡土氣的日本來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.56,0:11:24.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來…阿妮亞你修行的情況如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.97,0:11:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還順利嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.56,0:11:29.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？  我的修行很順利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初是比較辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在和城裡人的關係也搞得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一提起麗晶街後巷的占卜師阿妮亞的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.42,0:11:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也算是小有名氣啦…在一部分人當中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.90,0:11:41.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來你又怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.71,0:11:45.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被要求當老師這種你無法完成的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？  我也很順利啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.97,0:11:49.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？  照片我看過了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.99,0:11:51.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都是女孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？什麼意思嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:53.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:56.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不點又傻呼呼又土氣的涅吉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:12:01.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被一群漂亮的大姐姐圍著嘻嘻哈哈  哪還有心思修行了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  阿妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.51,0:12:06.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是打心裡在認真做老師這個工作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:09.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全是女生還不因為是女子學校  我又有什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我可沒有整天嘻嘻哈哈  身高也有見長哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.58,0:12:17.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也每天都有成長哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:20.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小不點不管再怎麼成長估計也沒差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.31,0:12:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.27,0:12:23.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要不要比一比？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.69,0:12:24.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:29.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算是大哥獲勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.35,0:12:30.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊  阿妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.08,0:12:38.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你踮腳了吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.87,0:12:41.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少找藉口了  我才沒踮腳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.85,0:12:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也不會輸你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.53,0:12:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是小孩子氣呢  傻瓜涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.00,0:12:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總說我是小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.15,0:12:53.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看這回阿妮亞才算是小不點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是小朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:57.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…這兩人本來就是小朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是令人欣慰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.67,0:13:03.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老師真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不準呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.16,0:13:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下搞不好危險了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:08.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.86,0:13:10.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉弟弟的態度啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:12.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還看不出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和那孩子說話時的涅吉非常隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.76,0:13:18.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說基本沒什麼顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.72,0:13:19.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且偶爾還會沒大沒小
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.43,0:13:26.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據我所知  只有對高畑老師和小太郎說話時  涅吉才會那麼隨意
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…對卡莫君也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:31.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對3-A的所有人毫無例外都是客客氣氣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.15,0:13:32.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是才注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:38.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉弟弟和3-A的所有同學之間都存在著內心障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.49,0:13:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內心障礙？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擊～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.79,0:13:42.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擊～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.74,0:13:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打擊～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.81,0:13:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而和那個孩子之間就不存在這層障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.91,0:13:49.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這代表什麼大家應該明白吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:50.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（就是說）
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.02,0:13:51.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑  太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:55.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你別吃得太快了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:59.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼！  一天到晚傻呼呼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看…飯都沾到臉上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:09.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不管怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.67,0:14:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞  很感謝你特地過來找我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.70,0:14:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不是為了你而來的呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.26,0:14:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是因為涅佳涅姐姐拜託我才來的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.03,0:14:22.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.01,0:14:23.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後跟涅吉老師配成對的可能性最大…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.37,0:14:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼情況？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:35.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸…幸會
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一堆女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.71,0:14:39.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…她們就是那些照片上的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.51,0:14:41.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行…不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:42.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能被擊倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.18,0:14:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面的印象很重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:48.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.78,0:14:49.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.83,0:14:51.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉的諸位學生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.55,0:14:52.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是安娜·可可羅瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.80,0:14:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請叫我阿妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.98,0:15:02.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情怎麼就複雜起來了呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.80,0:15:07.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實涅吉老師周圍的形勢真是越來越複雜了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:10.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過阿妮亞她滿可愛的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.58,0:15:11.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  確實
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.97,0:15:14.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.19,0:15:16.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是露天浴場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.89,0:15:19.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你們是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.87,0:15:24.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的同伴！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.51,0:15:29.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們好像知道魔法的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.45,0:15:32.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是的  我們都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.57,0:15:34.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我叫宮崎和香
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.72,0:15:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫綾瀨夕映
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.34,0:15:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.88,0:15:43.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…阿妮亞跟涅吉老師一樣  在倫敦修行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.68,0:15:45.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我修行的是占卜師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…阿妮亞你已經有搭檔了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過那個…契約…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,契…你們連這都知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:15:57.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情還沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:16:01.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選搭檔這種事情必須得慎重才行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.61,0:16:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅…涅吉他又如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.41,0:16:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會和那個叫明日菜什麼的已經做過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.47,0:16:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒可能的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.83,0:16:11.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傻瓜他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼說  明日菜她是敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:20.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為…為什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.56,0:16:24.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還用問嗎？  當然是因為胸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸大的女人都是敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.49,0:16:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.52,0:16:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對  男人總會被那種東西給騙得團團轉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:34.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對  所以要趕緊從這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  綾瀨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.32,0:16:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛  那小鬼是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.12,0:16:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老師的青梅竹馬不會就是她吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.33,0:16:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不大  但形狀很好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:51.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是美胸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.11,0:16:53.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女人也是敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:56.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:57.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她們一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:01.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對大海沒興趣  但我喜歡溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.19,0:17:03.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:05.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的敵人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.31,0:17:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  不是小阿妮亞嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:09.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛那一下搖得好誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:16.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊  那個孩子就是傳說中的阿妮亞？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:20.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你們三個已經打成一片啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.63,0:17:21.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.72,0:17:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本的溫泉感覺如何啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:26.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.99,0:17:29.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞  回頭我們互相擦背吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.97,0:17:30.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.69,0:17:32.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千鶴姐的胸部又變大了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.84,0:17:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼搞得啊  這個班級
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.49,0:17:37.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不是都只有15歲左右的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.12,0:17:41.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根本就是讓之前那個明日菜變得不值一提的巨乳軍團啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:45.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺氣！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.66,0:17:48.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不會輸給你這種小丫頭的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人雖然不是巨乳  但身材卻非常之好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.16,0:18:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咕  四面楚歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.28,0:18:04.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.71,0:18:06.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們另當別論
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.19,0:18:07.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.09,0:18:09.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們定能成為好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡…不必
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.02,0:18:19.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.91,0:18:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡怎麼搞的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.30,0:18:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就是一個巨乳巢穴嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.20,0:18:26.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再待在這種地方的話  涅吉肯定就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是得下定決心…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.07,0:18:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…趕快把涅吉給抓回威爾士去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.44,0:18:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快走了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.53,0:18:42.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是被發現了會怎麼樣你應該知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.19,0:18:43.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.36,0:18:48.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊  知不知道到底是多虧了誰你才能到這裡來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:49.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.70,0:18:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯什麼嗯  你根本沒在聽我說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.74,0:18:53.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.72,0:18:59.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  是誰擅自闖進禁咒書庫裡去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了  涅吉快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  沒事  馬上好…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕快！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.21,0:19:06.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊  趕快把書扔了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.83,0:19:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  馬上就能全記住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.07,0:19:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個傻瓜  快跑起來啊  難道你想被抓住啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.61,0:19:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  馬上就跑…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:14.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜傻瓜傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真受不了你這傢伙了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不在你就什麼事也做不好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.20,0:19:23.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.73,0:19:27.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  我到日本來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.75,0:19:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.83,0:19:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要把涅吉給帶回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.06,0:19:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  起來啦  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.25,0:19:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.25,0:19:37.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回鄉的準備已經做好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:40.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起來啦  趕快給我換…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.69,0:19:47.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說涅吉你又…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.12,0:19:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.33,0:19:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼鬼啊  涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Anya Flame Knuckle{\r}\N阿妮亞火焰鐵拳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.54,0:19:56.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！  為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  明日菜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.75,0:20:03.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老毛病又發作了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.94,0:20:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你這個傢伙一大清早的搞什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.50,0:20:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個女孩真火暴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.67,0:20:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.20,0:20:13.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.38,0:20:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟涅吉的姐姐很像嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.87,0:20:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到現在還是不那樣做就睡不著覺嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:21.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.27,0:20:22.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才只是因為睡迷糊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:23.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有明日菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:26.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是那個和涅佳涅姐很像的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.90,0:20:28.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…確實有那麼三分像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.33,0:20:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但姐姐她可沒你這副傻樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.11,0:20:33.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比你可漂亮多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.46,0:20:35.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再說一遍？  死小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然鑽到這個傻女人的被窩裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.86,0:20:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不純潔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.37,0:20:40.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.04,0:20:42.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說我那是不由自主…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難怪我總是討厭死小鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.12,0:20:46.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了啦  我們回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.90,0:20:48.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下啦  阿妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.43,0:20:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  阿妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.94,0:20:52.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天不是說了涅吉他現在還不能回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.01,0:20:53.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.92,0:20:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼權利對我指手畫腳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.78,0:21:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼權利…當然因為我是涅吉的搭…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:03.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼啊  你們兩個
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.68,0:21:05.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不行啦  明日菜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.54,0:21:07.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞她還沒那啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.54,0:21:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是知道我們所有人都做過了的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:13.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭是什麼意思？  大白癡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.33,0:21:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學  明日菜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.75,0:21:19.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好啊  卡莫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.77,0:21:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老師人在嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:23.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於卡片的功能方面我有點事情想請…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.28,0:21:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔  你們想做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓  噓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:30.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼  原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.67,0:21:32.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞啊  聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:34.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是很重要的事情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上啊…實際上呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.47,0:21:41.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡的所有七個女孩子竟然全都跟涅吉弟弟是搭…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.83,0:21:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟想說什麼東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.62,0:21:48.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想做什麼啊  春奈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.56,0:21:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲早會露餡的  有什麼關係嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.77,0:21:53.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之  我們走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.36,0:21:56.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞啊  為什麼那麼急著趕回去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.03,0:22:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說阿妮亞你喜歡涅吉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.90,0:22:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.26,0:22:06.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:13.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實  把涅吉一個人丟在這麼多女孩子中間是比較掛心啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.37,0:22:14.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.71,0:22:17.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.81,0:22:18.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.42,0:22:20.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.18,0:22:27.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是這樣呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.19,0:22:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.84,0:22:31.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來暫時就沒問題了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.67,0:22:34.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩下子呢  木乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.71,0:22:37.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是完美的危機應對能力  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.24,0:22:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊  那孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.42,0:22:48.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pacchi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.54,0:22:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Pactio吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.98,0:22:51.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.75,0:22:52.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:54.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.84,0:22:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不和大家一起玩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:22:57.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得來海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:22:58.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.39,0:22:59.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.44,0:23:02.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才完全不是那麼回事哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.54,0:23:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才？  什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.87,0:23:08.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她們說我喜歡你啊什麼的那個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.10,0:23:12.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那事？  那還用說嘛  阿妮亞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.21,0:23:14.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你這傢伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.61,0:23:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒和那些漂亮大姐姐中的誰卿卿我我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.37,0:23:21.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情當然不可能啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.28,0:23:24.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她們都是我的學生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.77,0:23:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.10,0:23:30.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就不纏著你要馬上回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.35,0:23:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.51,0:23:34.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.02,0:23:36.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不用強行帶他回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.89,0:23:42.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大清早那情形  怎麼想這裡的環境對涅吉的修行絕對不利
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:45.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  還是需要我在這裡好好看著他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這麼決定了  我們趕快回到大伙身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.63,0:23:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下…我說  別拉我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.28,0:23:51.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.68,0:23:53.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.07,0:24:01.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.06,0:24:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為人數突然增加  無法為你們提供第二晚的客房
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.32,0:24:09.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得不讓各位擠一個大房間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.00,0:24:11.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡  本來就是我們的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.25,0:24:14.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小事一樁  這樣反而更有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.60,0:24:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.27,0:24:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.58,0:24:20.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡涅吉弟弟身邊的人可要小心了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:24.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉弟弟啊  有時候沒有姐姐的溫暖就睡不著的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.08,0:24:27.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時睡迷糊之後可能會一下抱住旁邊的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.25,0:24:29.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木乃香同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.63,0:24:30.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次聽說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.09,0:24:31.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驚
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.38,0:24:35.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到涅吉老師竟然有這麼讓人又喜又羞的癖好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.16,0:24:37.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是個好機會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.89,0:24:42.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  我得好好看著  別讓他又犯早上的迷糊事
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.25,0:24:50.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰能夠睡在涅吉老師的旁邊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.51,0:24:51.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們來一決勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.73,0:24:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枕頭大戰啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.94,0:25:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久沒有和大小姐共枕了呢  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.03,0:25:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  小刹
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.59,0:25:05.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我們睡一床被子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.95,0:25:08.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這…這…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.81,0:25:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說！  你們這幫人給我老實睡覺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.66,0:25:19.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果呢  還沒決出勝負  大家就抱頭大睡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.38,0:25:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天晚上都瘋成那樣子不睏才怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.88,0:25:24.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也躺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.97,0:25:27.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼哼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.09,0:25:29.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能睡著呢  傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.37,0:25:31.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.54,0:25:34.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來就是要怎麼樣才能獲取涅吉身邊的位置了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.04,0:25:38.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾淨利索點哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.54,0:25:40.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼乾淨利索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.75,0:25:41.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈…哈嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.58,0:25:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼  這個殺氣是？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.37,0:25:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這幫大姐姐真打算去搶涅吉身邊的位置？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.71,0:25:51.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  盡可能自然一點
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.25,0:25:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊裝成睡相不好  一邊接近涅吉老師
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.00,0:26:00.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡  那幫人是認真的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.88,0:26:02.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.38,0:26:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.35,0:26:07.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去洗手間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.78,0:26:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  等下
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.76,0:26:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.35,0:26:26.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.79,0:26:28.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  糟糕  一不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.39,0:26:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…怎麼會…真是天上掉下的餡餅
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.79,0:26:39.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧  涅吉老師
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.33,0:26:43.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請用我溫暖的胸來…嗚
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.57,0:26:45.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  班長  我從小就睡相不太好…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.93,0:26:47.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰信啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.43,0:26:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…騙你玩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.78,0:26:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉弟弟我收下了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.86,0:26:55.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧  到我的胸懷裡來  涅吉弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.02,0:26:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Anya Over Head…{\r}\N阿妮亞倒掛金鉤…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.43,0:26:57.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.17,0:26:59.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}…Kick！{\r}\N…踢！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.96,0:27:02.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你對涅吉老師做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.69,0:27:03.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這小丫頭
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.94,0:27:06.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  挨那一下子涅吉死不了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.36,0:27:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.25,0:27:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還不醒…  啊  已經昏過去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.55,0:27:13.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.42,0:27:14.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好機會啊  和香
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.86,0:27:15.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上掉餡餅了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.48,0:27:17.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先請
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.30,0:27:26.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,涅…涅吉老師  和香不才…  請多…多…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.58,0:27:29.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.19,0:27:35.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不允許先偷吃！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.59,0:27:37.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和香
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.94,0:27:39.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這幫人…還是姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.93,0:27:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是有點變態啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.39,0:27:43.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛是不分年齡的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.65,0:27:47.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.15,0:28:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…發生什麼事了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.76,0:28:10.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道  我身體到處也疼得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.97,0:28:12.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別是頭上還腫了一個包
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.17,0:28:15.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我要告你！
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.41,0:28:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後  用網路訊息進行社會性抹殺
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.58,0:28:21.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…這一定是夢…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.49,0:28:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  那一定是個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.05,0:28:28.03,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（待續）
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.03,0:28:29.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說她最有可能!?
